node.text: “I like finding the rules and then figuring out ways to break them.” Go behind the scenes as the ultimate rule breaker, @finneas, explains his creative process and how the #ClashdeCartier collection inspired him to create a unique sound track for the special exhibition in Los Angeles. Open only from August 25th – September 1st, from 10AM – 7PM. Stop by to take home a limited-edition cassette from @finneas.
